      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@   DC호출
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3100-DJL4043-CALL-RTN.

      *@3.1.1 입력파라미터 조립
      *@처리내용:처리DC입력파라미터=
      *@SET(처리구분,조회기준일자)

      *    처리구분
           MOVE YNJL4043-PRCSS-DSTIC
             TO XDJL4043-I-PRCSS-DSTIC
      *    조회기준일자
           MOVE YNJL4043-BASE-YMD
             TO XDJL4043-I-BASE-YMD

      *@3.1.2 프로그램 호출
      *@처리내용:DC프로그램호출
           #DYCALL DJL4043 YCCOMMON-CA XDJL4043-CA

      *@3.1.3 처리결과CHECK
      *@실행조건:COND-XDJL4043-OK
      *@처리내용:리턴코드가 정상(00) 아닐경우 오류처리한다
           IF COND-XDJL4043-OK
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
              #ERROR XDJL4043-R-ERRCD
                     XDJL4043-R-TREAT-CD
                     XDJL4043-R-STAT
           END-IF
           .
       S3100-DJL4043-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
